After Local Pass

This is the sequence I’d follow:

1. ✅ Local Simulator E2E
2. Commit (Mobile + Backend + SQL)
3. Deploy Backend → Staging
4. Apply SQL migration on Staging
5. Staging E2E
6. Android Physical Device
7. iPhone Physical Device
8. Deploy Backend → Production (when Apple/Google review pauses)
9. Build IPA/APK v10 (only if required)

